28:51.466 --> 28:54.007
with Sting playing in the background and
all that, but who cares where we are?

28:54.041 --> 28:56.344
It's all about us, right?
Right, it's about us.

28:56.378 --> 28:58.346
Which is why I don't want
to do it on a night

28:58.380 --> 29:00.215
that you spent half of
dancing with another guy

29:00.389 --> 29:02.374
and that you're sober enough
to remember it the next day!

29:02.408 --> 29:05.878
Why are you yelling at me? Because I have never
felt less like being intimate with someone

29:05.904 --> 29:08.317
and either you can't tell
or you just don't care.

29:08.358 --> 29:09.844
(sighs)

29:11.120 --> 29:12.040
Where are you going?

29:12.059 --> 29:14.720
I'm sorry if I'm trying to
be spontaneous and fun.

29:19.201 --> 29:21.411
I think I'm just
gonna walk home.

29:22.832 --> 29:23.563
Blaine!

29:25.069 --> 29:26.779
(sighs):
God!

29:39.184 --> 29:41.749
(audience murmuring)

29:45.065 --> 29:47.502
