Maria has disappointed you.

29:47.704 --> 29:49.438
I'm still a virgin.

29:50.728 --> 29:52.892
And your Tony has
disappointed you.

29:52.901 --> 29:54.437
- Me, too.
- Look, the audience is smart.

29:54.472 --> 29:57.232
The only sensible solution is to
just cancel the show.

29:57.242 --> 30:00.560
I'd rather send everybody home than
give a false, inauthentic performance.

30:00.562 --> 30:02.167
Five minutes!

30:02.190 --> 30:05.729
