Blaine, tone down the blush.

30:05.744 --> 30:07.907
My eyebrows are fine.

30:20.765 --> 30:23.704
Artie? Artie, are you okay?
You look upset.

30:23.738 --> 30:25.255
Everything is wrong.

30:25.257 --> 30:27.245
The scenery, the costumes,
the staging.

30:27.256 --> 30:29.240
You know, I thought if I just
pretended like I knew

30:29.291 --> 30:31.012
