that I'm a fraud.

30:35.614 --> 30:37.575
Artie, you were brilliant.

30:37.609 --> 30:40.714
Really, this show is absolutely amazing,
and that is all thanks to you.

30:40.917 --> 30:44.702
It's awful.
I let everybody down.

30:44.722 --> 30:46.944
Hey, Artie, some of the cast needs
to talk to you before we go on.

30:48.572 --> 30:50.275
See? It's mutiny.

30:50.311 --> 30:52.444
Dude, we have a problem.

30:52.491 --> 30:56.478
